00:01:42.190 --> 00:01:47.190
We find then that the speed
in which the wave propagates--

00:01:47.190 --> 00:01:51.120
you pick one peak
of a wave, and you

00:01:51.120 --> 00:01:53.310
see how it propagates--
one point of variance

00:01:53.310 --> 00:01:54.270
here propagates.

00:01:54.270 --> 00:01:58.590
The speed in which it propagates
