equation to the Lorentz force,

00:02:29.470 --> 00:02:34.180
again, as a reminder, for
those who had had 8.02 already,

00:02:34.180 --> 00:02:35.705
the force on the
charged particle

00:02:35.705 --> 00:02:39.580
