field is given by 2 times

00:02:39.580 --> 00:02:43.270
E, plus 2 times V cross B.

00:02:43.270 --> 00:02:46.660
If you have two charges, the
force between those two charges

00:02:46.660 --> 00:02:51.160
is the product of the 2
divided by r squared, times 1

00:02:51.160 --> 00:02:52.570
over 4 pi x mu 0.

00:02:52.570 --> 00:02:54.950
Again, [INAUDIBLE].

00:02:54.950 --> 00:02:57.230
