00:06:27.550 --> 00:06:28.810
I do the same with t--

00:06:28.810 --> 00:06:31.110
I find minus c.

00:06:31.110 --> 00:06:35.940
I will use this second
derivatives of u.

00:06:35.940 --> 00:06:39.550
x and t are all 0.

00:06:39.550 --> 00:06:41.350
If I put this now
in my equation,

00:06:41.350 --> 00:06:50.930
I find second derivative of
f with u is of 1 minus c--

00:06:50.930 --> 00:06:58.950
